B.Ow=new A.a5("Task: Accomplish engine oil change in accordance with AMM 12-10-01. Record part numbers and batch numbers of oil used. Sign off upon completion.","G\xf6rev: AMM 12-10-01'e uygun olarak motor ya\u011f\u0131 de\u011fi\u015fimini ger\xe7ekle\u015ftirin. Kullan\u0131lan ya\u011f\u0131n par\xe7a numaralar\u0131n\u0131 ve seri numaralar\u0131n\u0131 kaydedin. Tamamland\u0131\u011f\u0131nda imzalay\u0131n.","Accomplish \u2026 in accordance with \u2026 Sign off upon completion")
