B.XB=new A.y(B.I,"Hava durumu havac\u0131l\u0131k i\xe7in kritiktir","Hava raporlar\u0131 ve navigasyon belgeleri y\xfcksek d\xfczeyde standardize edilmi\u015f kelime bilgisi kullan\u0131r. METAR, TAF, NOTAM ve ATIS, pilotlar\u0131n ve kontrol\xf6rlerin aninda anlamas\u0131 gereken belirli terimler i\xe7erir.\n\nBu ders, en s\u0131k s\u0131nanan hava durumu ve navigasyon terimlerini kapsar.",null,null,null)
B.Xx=new A.y(B.w,"\ud83c\udf26\ufe0f Hava Olaylar\u0131","**CAVOK** \u2014 Ceiling And Visibility OK (vis >10km, no cloud below 5000ft, no significant weather)\n**BECMG** \u2014 Becoming (gradual change within a period)\n**TEMPO** \u2014 Temporary fluctuations lasting less than 1 hour\n**CB** \u2014 Cumulonimbus (thunderstorm cloud, avoid by 20nm)\n**TSRA** \u2014 Thunderstorm with rain\n**FG** \u2014 Fog | **BR** \u2014 Mist | **RA** \u2014 Rain | **SN** \u2014 Snow",null,null,null)
