B.W9=new A.y(B.I,"IFR clearance neden okunur?",'IFR (Instrument Flight Rules) u\xe7u\u015flar i\xe7in ATC, kalk\u0131\u015ftan \xf6nce kapsaml\u0131 bir "clearance" mesaj\u0131 verir. Bu mesaj, u\xe7a\u011f\u0131n t\xfcm rota bilgisini, k\u0131s\u0131tlamalar\u0131 ve prosed\xfcrleri i\xe7erir.\n\nPilotun clearance\'\u0131 tam ve do\u011fru \u015fekilde "readback" (geri okumas\u0131) zorunludur \u2014 hata varsa ATC d\xfczeltir.',null,null,null)
B.Uq=new A.y(B.w,"\ud83d\udccb CRAFT Format\u0131",'IFR clearance\'\u0131 hat\u0131rlamak i\xe7in **CRAFT** k\u0131saltmas\u0131 kullan\u0131l\u0131r:\n\n**C** \u2192 **Clearance limit** (hedef havaliman\u0131 veya fix)\n**R** \u2192 **Route** (rota \u2014 SID + airways + STAR)\n**A** \u2192 **Altitude** (ba\u015flang\u0131\xe7 y\xfcksekli\u011fi / FL)\n**F** \u2192 **Frequency** (ilk frekans)\n**T** \u2192 **Transponder code** (squawk)\n\n**Yayg\u0131n ifadeler:**\n\u2022 "Cleared to [destination] via [route]" \u2192 rotay\u0131 ver\n\u2022 "Climb via SID" \u2192 SID ile t\u0131rman (irtifa k\u0131s\u0131tlamalar\u0131 dahil)\n\u2022 "Expect [FL] ten minutes after departure" \u2192 kalk\u0131\u015ftan 10 dk sonra [FL] bekle\n\u2022 "Departure frequency [xxx.x]" \u2192 kalk\u0131\u015f frekans\u0131\n\u2022 "Readback correct" \u2192 geri okuma do\u011fru',null,null,null)
B.Nq=new A.a5('"Turkish 234, cleared to London Heathrow via KEMAL3A departure, then airways L602, Upper Blue 2, expect flight level 370 ten minutes after departure, departure frequency 119.1, squawk 2374."',"C=Heathrow, R=KEMAL3A+L602+UB2, A=ba\u015flang\u0131\xe7 SID, bekle FL370, F=119.1, T=2374","cleared to \u2026 via \u2026 expect \u2026 departure frequency \u2026 squawk")
